水平都較正常高。<br />\n<br />\n受背景污染較高的氣團影響，日間的陽光有利光化煙霧現象，令臭氧及微細懸浮粒子在珠江三角洲區域內迅速形成，現時多區包括荃灣、屯門及大埔等，空氣質素健康指數已達9，而東涌更至10。<br />\n<br />\n環保署呼籲，當健康風險級別達到甚高或嚴重水平時，一般市民應減少在戶外逗留及體力消耗。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"又要準備爆發第二波肺炎"},{"pid":"f7cbb473741c8d0d95bf1346691067a9f4c222b1","tid":1989685,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0DS4Fz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0DS4Fz.jpg&h=ae373be1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38390b20561451a9db8f8d6bb007e064f812f77c","tid":1989685,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7cbb473741c8d0d95bf1346691067a9f4c222b1","tid":1989685,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0DS4Fz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0DS4Fz.jpg&h=ae373be1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T10:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}